{"tid":1815770,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Android高手/用家請入","createTime":"2020-01-07T18:36:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T13:50:24.000Z","uid":312076,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"818c623031830f1add0842bef7c3256819b588a4","tid":1815770,"uid":312076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T18:36:56.000Z","msg":"是咁的，細路我用緊s8+，到目前為止冇任何<br />\n<br />\nlag,crash等問題，對samsung呢幾年<br />\n<br />\nhardware同software都頗為滿意，本身諗住<br />\n<br />\n就算換機都唔轉牌子，但近期兩件事令我動<br />\n<br />\n搖，所以想集中一次過問，希望各路android<br />\n<br />\n高手同各大牌子用家能夠比少少意見。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1.亦都係最大問題，共狗360軟件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。Reddit<br />\n<br />\n個Po話除咗ADB或其他方法，否則無法移<br />\n<br />\n除。小弟對呢方面毫無認識，google過亦睇<br />\n<br />\n唔明，請問Android高手可唔可以簡單講吓大<br />\n<br />\n概係咩一回事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />實際操作難度大唔大？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.冇3.5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個我完全唔get<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> iPhone 就話<br />\n<br />\nlightning有錢收 點解Android都要跟？仲要不<br />\n<br />\n約而同旗艦機冇而中階機有(s10/note10 lite<br />\n<br />\n，sony<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，睇嚟唯有硬食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。所以想問吓其他用緊其他廠商嘅<br />\n<br />\n巴絲意見(其實好似得返sony lg google)，尤<br />\n<br />\n其係旗艦機用家，對自己部電話有咩評價，有<br />\n<br />\n冇伏位等。(大陸機唔駛出聲，我就係想解決<br />\n<br />\n共狗spy緊我呢個問題)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論"},{"pid":"1211d5d8beeb7c2687fa78d2a199bc59b7875571","tid":1815770,"uid":255744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T18:44:30.000Z","msg":"sony就快3.5mm回歸"},{"pid":"a942ca5149b6d435241d2a902269e35bc22c9cfa","tid":1815770,"uid":312076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1211d5d8beeb7c2687fa78d2a199bc59b7875571","tid":1815770,"uid":255744,"like":0,"dislike":